e are not superpowered in terms of gameplay as in the first game, we have the ability to put words in a fast and logical way :) and the game has a dlc package called farewell. Last time we can see Chloe and Max as kids with this dlc We select the selections with the wasd keys, not the mouse control as in the first game. Instead of taking photos as an optional task, 2 types of graffiti have been introduced. Since we do not have special power like Max, the \"Backtalk\" feature was introduced. With this feature, we can make the people in front of us do something we want and we can get rid of it. We do this with the other person by entering a rational and fast spoken contest.", "appid": "554620", "steamid": "profiles/76561198102381081", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "75", "votes_funny": "4", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1577361600.0}
