{"text": "First of all I really enjoyed every Dark Souls there is, but Sekiro is just on another level. It has an insane atmosphere and landscape. I ain't no japanologist nor do I know the Japanese mythology but to me Sekiro felt like a timetravel right back to these ages of samurai and all the mythical stories of that time. All bosses are a demanding but also so rewarding after you beat them. It's a lot of fun", "appid": "814380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198263055684", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1578830400.0}
{"text": "Epizod Pierwszy do drugiego HL2 jest całkiem spoko. Rozwijał dalej fabułe, poznaliśmy bliżej Alyx Vance, dodano nowego przeciwnika: Zombikombinat, który może nieoczekiwanie wyjąć granat, oraz dostajemy flary dzięki którym możemy podpalać wrogów. Co tu dalej mówić, nie będę dalej zdradzał żeby nie robić spoilerów. Niestety zakończenie mało satysfakcjonujące oraz gierka jest dość krótka: można gre ukończyć w 3-4,5 godziny, można sobie gre wydłużyć zdobywając osiągnięcia których nie udało sie zdobyć za pierwszym razem. 29 zł to nie jest dużo, ale wolałbym kupić Episode One na przecenie (chyba niecałe 6 zł). O i chciałbym podziękować mojemu znaj za kupienie mi dwóch epizodów do Half-Life'a. MOGE POLECIĆ EP1 (Thank you Relingkwish).", "appid": "380", "steamid": "profiles/76561198859038609", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "6", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1598184000.0}
{"text": "So this game is a hunt game where 1 player is a monster which must eat to be stronger, so he can destroy a power relay and 4 players are hunters whose task is to kill the monster before it gets to stage 3(the highest one), if they fail they will have to kill it anyway but it gets way more difficult. This game offers good graphics, some nice, enjoyable gameplay, a quite impressive amount of hunters and monsters ,different maps where one of the sides has bigger advantage. AND ITS FREE. (Probably because a few people would buy it) I personally encountered some problems with the audio, some sudden beeps and scratches idk from where, but i think I'm the only one with that problem. Overall one of the best free games you can get on steam.  My rating: 7.5", "appid": "273350", "steamid": "profiles/76561198086980642", "voted_up": true, "votes_up": "25", "votes_funny": "1", "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1487505600.0}
