ct, if a game charges you x4 the amount you set in the pre-authorized, steam WILL/DOES allow any game to by pass this limit. When you questioned them about this, they just give you the useless info page about how subs work, if you reply there is no info on there about steam going above the pre authorized amount, and they'll close your ticket, be safe and dont put too much money on steam as steam and these shady companies work together with policy's and TOS  to steal it and do everything not to give it back.", "appid": "719640", "steamid": "profiles/76561197975931257", "voted_up": false, "votes_up": "16", "votes_funny": 0, "early_access": false, "tstamp_created": 1581163200.0}
